"{\"uid\": \"kpcw.org-park-city-2024-03-21-gov-cox-calls-olympics-a-smart-investment-hopes-to-become-part-of-rotation\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Gov.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 4, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cox said Thursday more countries would be vying to host the Olympics if they were in the same position as Utah.\", \"from\": 5, \"to\": 116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 111, \"end\": 115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"score\": 0.9995282441900354, \"rank\": 0.00045287994439937516, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I promise you that if every country had the infrastructure that we had, they would see it as a smart investment,\\\" Cox said.\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 242, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The reason that some countries have decided not to do it is because they have to build all of these venues.\", \"from\": 243, \"to\": 351, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's very expensive, and then the venues do not get used, and they end up getting torn down.\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 450, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's clearly a waste\\u2026 We are so fortunate not to have that problem or issue.\\\"\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 534, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee has named Salt Lake City as the preferred host for the Winter Olympics in 2034, but that will not be officially decided until the summer.\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 540, \"end\": 571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 582, \"end\": 596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"score\": 0.9932557604378749, \"rank\": 0.0067702665862596715, \"text\": \"Salt Lake City\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC has not officially recognized any other host cities for the 2034 Games.\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 789, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 714, \"end\": 717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.999999999982947, \"rank\": 6.947328391022213e-12, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC has discussed establishing arotation of hostsfor the Winter Games, amid concerns about climate change and declining snowfall.\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 924, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 795, \"end\": 798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.999999999982947, \"rank\": 6.947328391022213e-12, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cox said Utah could be a contender in that cycle.\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 935, \"end\": 939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"score\": 0.9995282441900354, \"rank\": 0.00045287994439937516, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My hope is, and there is certainly been talk of this, that over the course of the next few years that the IOC will make a decision to kind of have a set group of cities to host the Olympics.\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1084, \"end\": 1087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.999999999982947, \"rank\": 6.947328391022213e-12, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So that every 20 years maybe, or every 16, we come back to these host cities and that Salt Lake City will be one of those.\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1291, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1255, \"end\": 1269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"score\": 0.9932557604378749, \"rank\": 0.0067702665862596715, \"text\": \"Salt Lake City\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can envision one where you have an Asian Winter Games, a European Winter Games, a North American Winter Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1382, \"end\": 1390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999820797723239, \"rank\": 1.5067833641691104e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The governor said he hopes to be in Paris this summer when the IOC is expected to award the 2034 Olympics on Pioneer Day, July 24.\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1443, \"end\": 1448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999562374162252, \"rank\": 4.3764498955677695e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1470, \"end\": 1473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.999999999982947, \"rank\": 6.947328391022213e-12, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}]}"